1
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:26,070
Call me big brother.

2
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:35,740
Big brother.

3
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:56,930
It's Mom.

4
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:59,180
What does Mom want?

5
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:02,310
Hey, Hinata. How's everything?

6
00:01:02,650 --> 00:01:05,860
This is sudden. I'm doing fine...

7
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:09,610
Are you two brothers getting along?

8
00:01:09,610 --> 00:01:12,490
Why are you calling?
If you have nothing to say, I'm hanging up.

9
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:13,660
We're getting along great!

10
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:20,370
Oh, Mizuki, you're there too?
I'm so glad you two get along.

11
00:01:20,370 --> 00:01:25,960
I was worried when I remarried,
but I guess I had nothing to worry about!

12
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,710
Okay, okay! I get it.

13
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:31,470
You graduated from college,
and you start work next week, right?

14
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:37,890
Mizuki is going to grad school!
Even on different paths, you both must do your best!

15
00:01:37,890 --> 00:01:41,430
We'll be fine! Don't worry!

16
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:42,640
Talk to you later, then.

17
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,980
Ah, wait, hold on...

18
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:48,530
Are we really going to be fine?

19
00:01:48,980 --> 00:01:50,150
What do you mean?

20
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:52,610
Never mind.

21
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,790
I'm going to take a shower.

22
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,560
Hinata? What's wrong?

23
00:02:24,100 --> 00:02:25,190
Hinata?

24
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:26,690
Hinata?

25
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:29,940
Hinata?!
